{"tid":742874,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知點接受男朋友","createTime":"2018-07-15T03:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T06:34:04.000Z","uid":162332,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5870e7676057e08b52574334552a48fa5fc0ecec","tid":742874,"uid":162332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"同男朋友分手一個月後佢無啦啦搵返我，我其實都仲對佢有小小感覺嘅，但復合返先發現原來佢之前同我分手唔夠一個星期就同左第二個一齊，仲上埋牀，佢地兩個星期後散左。   之後我男朋友發現自己原來仲係好愛我就搵返我一齊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知道左之後真係好嬲，但我知佢唔算係岀軌，個段期間真係分手，但我接受唔到佢散左一個星期已經同第二個女仔一齊，一方面又話忘記唔到我，佢話因爲個時佢都唔開心，所以同第二個一齊想快啲忘記我，只係自己忘記唔到又想同返我一齊。<br />\n我有問佢，如果佢同女仔係夾嘅會唔會繼續一齊而唔會搵返我，佢話有可能，但佢都估唔到自己最後都係想返黎我身邊。<br />\n佢依個究竟係咩諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fea2a0bf288fe95588ed23d87f1b5a8f57f75fc","tid":742874,"uid":33053,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"你只係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ac0c704b48f5a1b4666f65df05ab51ccbffbe0","tid":742874,"uid":117947,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"好馬不吃回頭草<br />\n唔好俾人玩啦"},{"pid":"d317b8296132c0913fe8ce56c5b544cb387713d7","tid":742874,"uid":122709,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"當你免費雞屌住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵到下個再飛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c009488f31509e66e7b89e6838b3e518b5c9f5a4","tid":742874,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"因咩事分手？"},{"pid":"c2037ff05810a36ff49acebf356ebbf51b6838d2","tid":742874,"uid":162332,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fea2a0bf288fe95588ed23d87f1b5a8f57f75fc","tid":742874,"uid":33053,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy